==评价==
=== 票房 ===
影片在美国865家剧院上映，首周末票房达433,611美元，位列票房榜第八位<ref name=opening>{{cite news|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|date=2021-03-12|url=https://deadline.com/2021/03/raya-and-the-last-dragon-weekend-box-office-los-angeles-movie-theaters-reopening-1234713807/|title='Raya And The Last Dragon' Eyeing $5.7M Second Weekend B.O. As Exhibition Slowly Repairs|website=Deadline Hollywood|access-date=2021-03-12|archive-date=2021-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317215001/https://deadline.com/2021/03/raya-and-the-last-dragon-weekend-box-office-los-angeles-movie-theaters-reopening-1234713807/|dead-url=no}}</ref>；次周获六项奥斯卡提名，扩映至937家影院，票房达35.5万美元<ref>{{cite news|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|date=2021-03-21|url=https://deadline.com/2021/03/weekend-box-office-kelly-marie-tran-los-angeles-raya-and-the-last-dragon-1234718593/|title=L.A. Weekend Box Office Clears $1M+; Kelly Marie Tran & Carlos Lopez Estrada Welcome ‘Raya’ El Capitan Fans As Pic Posts Firm No. 1 Hold – Update|website=Deadline Hollywood|access-date=2021-03-21|archive-date=2021-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323155232/https://deadline.com/2021/03/weekend-box-office-kelly-marie-tran-los-angeles-raya-and-the-last-dragon-1234718593/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 专业评价 ===
[[汇总媒体|汇总媒体]][[烂番茄|烂番茄]]收录164条评论，打出99%的新鲜度，平均得分8.7/10。网站共识写道：“星光璀璨的演出阵容及编剧兼导演佛罗莱恩·泽勒出色的导演工作，让《困在时间里的父亲》动情演绎了失智症患者的形象<ref>{{cite web|title= The Father (2020)|url= https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_father_2020|website= Rotten Tomatoes|language= en|access-date= 2021-03-22|archive-date= 2020-12-09|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201209104237/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_father_2020|dead-url= no}}</ref>。”[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]收录41条评论，平均分88/100，表示“普遍好评”<ref>{{cite web |title=The Father Reviews |url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-father |website=Metacritic |access-date=2021-03-22 |archive-date=2020-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812224644/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-father |dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{tsl|en|PostTrak|PostTrak}}观众评分84%，观众推荐度54%<ref name=opening/>。

《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》的{{tsl|en|Owen Gleiberman|欧文·格里伯曼}}表示，“《困在时间里的父亲》是少数能够如此深刻、全面展现老年人心理状况恶化的影片，用看似合理、连贯的体验，让我们记住失智者的形象<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2020/film/reviews/the-father-review-anthony-hopkins-olivia-colman-1203482695/|title='The Father': Film Review|date=2020-01-27|first=Owen|last=Gleiberman|website=Variety|access-date=2021-02-11|archive-date=2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209130737/https://variety.com/2020/film/reviews/the-father-review-anthony-hopkins-olivia-colman-1203482695/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”《[[卫报|卫报]]》的本杰明·李（Benjamin Lee）认为霍普金斯的表演“惊人”、“打动人心”，能看到他很理性地跟自己和周围人的解释自己经历的事情。有几个让人感到不安的镜头是说他的世界发生了转变，但他岿然不动，或许只有聋人，才能够理解他每天醒来会经历什么样的问题。他认为，霍普金斯的情绪从愤怒到狂怒，到出离愤怒，再到沮丧，让人感觉他并不是在扮演一个构造成熟的角色，尽管我们会把他和丰富的演艺经历联系起来<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2020/jan/27/the-father-review-anthony-hopkins-olivia-colman|title=The Father review – Anthony Hopkins drives devastating dementia drama|date=2020-01-27|first=Benjamin|last=Lee|website=The Guardian|access-date=2021-02-11|archive-date=2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209130837/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2020/jan/27/the-father-review-anthony-hopkins-olivia-colman|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《[[好莱坞报道者|好莱坞报道者]]》的[[陶德·麥卡錫|陶德·麥卡錫]]认为影片是“自八年前的《[[爱_(法语电影)|爱]]》以来，讲述老年人境况最出色的电影，非常有见地、微妙、细腻地展现侵蚀性失智症，以及这个病对患者所造成的损害。安东尼·霍普金斯这位令人骄傲的英国演员出色展示了否认患有此病的形象，出彩的表现给法国作家佛罗莱恩·泽勒的导演处女作添上浓墨重彩的一笔<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/father-review-1273990|title='The Father': Film Review {{!}} Sundance 2020|date=2020-01-27|first=Todd|last=McCarthy|website=The Hollywood Reporter|access-date=2021-02-11|archive-date=2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209105737/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/father-review-1273990|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]的大卫·埃里希（David Ehrlich）认为，“泽勒改编他的同名获奖戏剧，慧眼独具，自信非凡，仿佛用镜头展现了他的一生。在泽勒看来，迷失自我的老年人朝他的女儿和看护發火，是再常见不过的事情，但这种场景逐渐体现出影片对思想的深入研究，展现出看着某人溺水时难以形容的痛苦<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2020/12/best-first-films-of-2020-1234604275/|title=The Best First Films of 2020 — Year in Review|date=2020-12-12|first1=Eric|last1=Kohn|first2=Kate|last2=Erbland|first3=David|last3=Ehrlich|website=IndieWire|access-date=2021-02-11|archive-date=2021-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210625035433/https://www.indiewire.com/2020/12/best-first-films-of-2020-1234604275/}}</ref>。”

《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》的珍妮特·卡特苏里斯（Jeannette Catsoulis）认为影片“非常有力、打动人”，大气地描绘了世界崩塌时的景象<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/02/25/movies/the-father-review.html|title='The Father' Review: A Capricious Mind|work=The New York Times|first=Jeanette|last=Catsoulis|date=2021-02-25|access-date=2021-03-15|archive-date=2021-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317215322/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/02/25/movies/the-father-review.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

